@host = http://localhost:5108
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### Health check (no auth)
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 1) Login — copy accessToken from response into @token above
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "amal123@gmail.com",
  "password": "amal12345678"
}

###

### 2) AI suggestions — requires @token
POST {{host}}/api/ai/suggestions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "I need to improve my confidence",
  "description": ""
}

###

### Swagger
GET {{host}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json
